		{
			dependencies: ["7A02000000000103"]
			description: [
				"&8[ SITE REPORT — HEAVY INDUSTRY ]&r"
				""
				"&7The coke ovens were only the furnace of a much larger operation. The presses and crushers that survive are built to a scale one person was never meant to operate alone.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: assemble the Immersive multiblocks — a Metal Press, a Crusher, a Squeezer.&r"
			]
			id: "7A0200000000010A"
