		{
			dependencies: ["7A0200000000010A"]
			description: [
				"&8[ SURVEY NOTE — THE OIL BENEATH ]&r"
				""
				"&7They did not stop at what could be dug. They drilled. There are dry boreholes across the map, capped and abandoned, that reach deeper than any mine.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: raise a Pumpjack over an oil deposit and refine what comes up in a Distillation Tower.&r"
