				"&8[ CROSS-REFERENCE — PRESSURE ]&r"
				""
				"&7One recovered facility ran on none of the usual power. It ran on compressed air, pushed through tubing, and on a strange mouldable material they made in quantity.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: pressurise — an Air Compressor, pressure tubing, a gauge, and your first Plastic.&r"
