		{
			dependencies: ["7A0200000000010D"]
			description: [
				"&8[ CROSS-REFERENCE — DISTANCE MEANT NOTHING ]&r"
				""
				"&7By the end, they had stopped moving materials at all. They moved them&r &8instantly&r&7. A logistics network with no carts, no rails, no distance. And the generators to feed it never stopped burning.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: a Teleporter, a QIO Dashboard, a Gas-Burning Generator. Make distance stop mattering.&r"
